data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the South Roebuck/Roebuck Springs!  This outstanding property is ready for a new owner and eagerly awaiting your offer. Located in a highly desirable area, this house offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful and friendly neighborhood, while being conveniently close to all amenities.  3 bedroom, 2 bath home with original hardwood floors and STORAGE!!! Main Bedroom has 2 large closets with attached bath. Bedrooms 2 and 3 also have large closets with plenty of storage.  The shared bath has an oversized vanity, shower/tub combo that was recently refinished, and a linen closet.  Step outside onto the inviting patio, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or host BBQs with family and friends. Plenty of room to be the host with the most! The backyard offers ample space for gardening or creating your own outdoor oasis. The attached garage provides convenient parking and additional storage options. This house is waiting for your personal touch!
